snippet.title: Matrix of Life
snippet.description:
Hello, dear viewers!  My given name is Ekaterina, but my clients call me Ange. 
I have been studying how to read signs and symbols for more than 10 years and I am reading Tarot cards since the age of 6. ​
Someone says I am a psychic, but it’s very easy to predict the future if you know karmic laws and listening to your intuition. 
You are free to choose, but you are not free from the consequences of your choice! At the coaching sessions, I am guiding you to success using ancient knowledge of karmic management. With my guidance, you are literally planting your success! 
Another Sacral tool in my hands is a Matrix of Life. 
I am highly educated in multiple subjects: Psychology, Numerology, Astrology. Symbolism, Regression Hypnoses, Vastu, Esoteric Subjects. Anyone coming into contact with me sees positive changes in their lives. I am the MASTER OF TRANSFORMATIONS, this is MY SUPERPOWER! Please, read and agree to the DISCLAIMER msg under my videos before contacting me!
